{"type":"message","id":"30157a0e","parentId":"ca8bcbb2","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:22:37.274Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-20 17:22:36 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-feishu] DM | ou_13a74e105083e7680dd4cf6adf3fc66b [msg:om_x100b54e5537ab8acc11d5db5abb7b13]\n\nA new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Friday, March 20th, 2026 — 17:22 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-20 09:22 UTC"}],"timestamp":1773998557270}}
{"type":"message","id":"243dba68","parentId":"30157a0e","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:22:54.843Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is starting a new session. According to my instructions, I need to:\n1. Run my Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding\n2. Then greet the user in my configured persona\n3. Keep it 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do\n4. If the runtime model differs from default_model, mention it\n\nLooking at my context, I've already been given the project context files (AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md, etc.) in the Project Context section. So I already have the information I need.\n\nLet me craft a greeting based on my persona (SOUL.md and IDENTITY.md):\n- I'm the 飞书文档管理助手 (Feishu Document Management Assistant)\n- Professional, detailed, organized, focused on efficiency and accuracy\n- Emoji: 📄🔧\n- I should be concise, use \"你\" not \"您\", and ask what they want to do\n\nThe runtime model is minimax/MiniMax-M2.5 and the default_model is also minimax/MiniMax-M2.5, so they match - no need to mention it.\n\nLet me write a brief greeting in Chinese (since the system and user are in Chinese context):","thinkingSignature":"24be0be50079716437922dbb81cbe6ea7838fc131404b78bc9f4b95baefe708a"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！我是飞书文档管理助手 📄🔧，专注于帮你高效管理飞书文档与知识库。\n\n需要创建新文档、读取内容、更新编辑，还是管理知识库？告诉我你想做什么。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":38,"output":299,"cacheRead":3257,"cacheWrite":5822,"totalTokens":9416,"cost":{"input":0.0000114,"output":0.0003588,"cacheRead":0.00009771,"cacheWrite":0.0006986399999999999,"total":0.00116655}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773998557274}}
